{"tid":1384091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望各位連登仔出post注意下自己用字","createTime":"2019-07-29T23:53:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T01:28:00.000Z","uid":185085,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"17e8925d59e7c3c176b588212fdca05499acc500","tid":1384091,"uid":185085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:53:39.000Z","msg":"因為你每句說話都好影響睇連登既人，由其大家心情已經好復雜，希望大家可以試下改改。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">標題：</span></span><br />\n標題方面盡量避免用帶有負能量同失敗主義用字<br />\n例如：我地場運動散緊、xxx俾你地害死、完全無人出黎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">內文：</span></span><br />\n內文方面盡量避免用互相指罵既用字<br />\n例如：xxx係鬼、xxx推人去死<br />\n<br />\n希望大家能夠從幫助運動既角度出發，唔好用一啲嘩眾取寵既句子。"},{"pid":"cfa291425935a586aac61a4ce927ec7cd6fccb7b","tid":1384091,"uid":185085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:06:21.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"7f26c6bc0141d77ccd3d3bcdc9beb56cbb8fdc6c","tid":1384091,"uid":189015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:07:07.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"059c531d2a5f92ea0a14ab90e3b059f617fdb1fb","tid":1384091,"uid":264215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:13:54.000Z","msg":"都唔知人地係鬼定唔識規矩<br />\n一嘢屌撚走曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地想幫都幫唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed97a58e2ff0af67020dc5b00b3105da25748495","tid":1384091,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f36d3a11ac508cb0cbad434324f88701ca618f","tid":1384091,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:16:09.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"bdd007d39a19ced96e350531286dc99dbfc62d90","tid":1384091,"uid":185085,"like":0,"disli